tid":699110,"uid":15428,"like":1,"dislike":22,"score":-21,"quote":{"pid":"c1d0211d7fed1edafcd3e72a6130c177f617593a","tid":699110,"uid":83194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d21c20eac867510f9ecf6c1f92045255b0677b8","tid":699110,"uid":15428,"like":1,"dislike":55,"score":-54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:12:08.000Z","msg":"做定期不如做儲蓄plan，風險低又可以保本抗通漲<br />\n<br />\ntg @omfghk"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:15:43.000Z","msg":"有咩plan咪拎出黎講"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T12:33:00.000Z","msg":"如果後生仔想儲得開心啲嘅有M嘅LV Plan<br />\n因為通常出面slogan就話「日儲$100年派$10000」<br />\n其實就係以每個月儲三千為例子，由第二年開始保證每年派一皮嘢派到一百歲<br />\n（供款年期可揀5/8/12/15年）<br />\nRef: <a href=\"https://www.manulife.com.hk/wps/wcm/connect/pws/fb4bb25e-0c02-43fb-8a31-0d28a418348b/Manulife_LaVie_Brochure_Chi_final_page.pdf?MOD=AJPERES\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.manulife.com.hk%2Fwps%2Fwcm%2Fconnect%2Fpws%2Ffb4bb25e-0c02-43fb-8a31-0d28a418348b%2FManulife_LaVie_Brochure_Chi_final_page.pdf%3FMOD%3DAJPERES&d=ZzA5IRrzd3BZ%2FN4D7BApPRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=139f3db7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.manulife.com.hk/wps/wcm/connect/pws/fb4bb25e-0c02-43fb-8a31-0d28a418348b/Manulife_LaVie_Brochure_Chi_final_page.pdf?MOD=AJPERES</a><br />\n<br />\n豬b就好在係每日複利息咁計，年期一般揀20(仲有5/10)<br />\n長遠回報係比較有優勢同吸引<br />\n但起步年期的階段就令了解唔深嘅初學者卻步<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.chubb.com/hk-zh/_assets/documents/p137_golden_touch_premier_saver_chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.chubb.com%2Fhk-zh%2F_assets%2Fdocuments%2Fp137_golden_touch_premier_saver_chi.pdf&d=ZzA5IRrzd3BZ%2FN4D7BApPRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d712e79c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.chubb.com/hk-zh/_assets/documents/p137_golden_touch_premier_saver_chi.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n當然仲有其他Plan都唔差<br />\n同埋，同電視推廣理財理念一樣，要明白儲蓄plan係for長遠回報，須持續供款至某年期<br />\n（短期內退保會令價值受損，所以要決定時要了解清楚、諗清楚）<br />\n<br />\n利申：IFA，市面上講得出嘅保險公司大多都做得到<br />\n<br />\n基本概念可睇「錢家有道」：<a href=\"https://www.thechinfamily.hk/web/tc/managing-your-money/savings.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thechinfamily.hk%2Fweb%2Ftc%2Fmanaging-your-money%2Fsavings.html&d=ZzA5IRrzd3BZ%2FN4D7BApPRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=4c99da33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thechinfamily.hk/web/tc/managing-your-money/savings.html</a>"},{"pid":"1130ee2fb733aa233cfdf86538f760c8ad187e0c","tid":699110,"uid":83194,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"887974a9f13d9f99ce78d9fe34bf4760d4e28d0b","tid":699110,"uid":15428,"like":1,"dislike":22,"score":-21,"quote":{"pid":"c1d0211d7fed1edafcd3e72a6130c177f617593a","tid":699110,"uid":83194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d21c20eac867510f9ecf6c1f92045255b0677b8","tid":699110,"uid":15428,"like":1,"dislike":55,"score":-54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:12:08.000Z","msg":"做定期不如做儲蓄plan，風險低又可以保本抗通漲<br />\n<br />\ntg @omfghk"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:15:43.000Z","msg":"有咩plan咪拎出黎講"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T12:33:00.000Z","msg":"如果後生仔想儲得開心啲嘅有M嘅LV Plan<br />\n因為通常出面slogan就話「日儲$100年派$10000」<br />\n其實就係以每個月儲三千為例子，由第二年開始保證每年派一皮嘢派到一百歲<br />\n（供款年期可揀5/8/12/15年）<br />\nRef: <a href=\"https://www.manulife.com.hk/wps/wcm/connect/pws/fb4bb25e-0c02-43fb-8a31-0d28a418348b/Manulife_LaVie_Brochure_Chi_final_page.pdf?MOD=AJPERES\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.manulife.com.hk%2Fwps%2Fwcm%2Fconnect%2Fpws%2Ffb4bb25e-0c02-43fb-8a31-0d28a418348b%2FManulife_LaVie_Brochure_Chi_final_page.pdf%3FMOD%3DAJPERES&d=ZzA5IRrzd3BZ%2FN4D7BApPRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=139f3db7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.manulife.com.hk/wps/wcm/connect/pws/fb4bb25e-0c02-43fb-8a31-0d28a418348b/Manulife_LaVie_Brochure_Chi_final_page.pdf?MOD=AJPERES</a><br />\n<br />\n豬b就好在係每日複利息咁計，年期一般揀20(仲有5/10)<br />\n長遠回報係比較有優勢同吸引<br />\n但起步年期的階段就令了解唔深嘅初學者卻步<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.chubb.com/hk-zh/_assets/documents/p137_golden_touch_premier_saver_chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.chubb.com%2Fhk-zh%2F_assets%2Fdocuments%2Fp137_golden_touch_premier_saver_chi.pdf&d=ZzA5IRrzd3BZ%2FN4D7BApPRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d712e79c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.chubb.com/hk-zh/_assets/documents/p137_golden_touch_premier_saver_chi.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n當然仲有其他Plan都唔差<br />\n同埋，同電視推廣理財理念一樣，要明白儲蓄plan係for長遠回報，須持續供款至某年期<br />\n（短期內退保會令價值受損，所以要決定時要了解清楚、諗清楚）<br />\n<br />\n利申：IFA，市面上講得出嘅保險公司大多都做得到<br />\n<br />\n基本概念可睇「錢家有道」：<a href=\"https://www.thechinfamily.hk/web/tc/managing-your-money/savings.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thechinfamily.hk%2Fweb%2Ftc%2Fmanaging-your-money%2Fsavings.html&d=ZzA5IRrzd3BZ%2FN4D7BApPRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=4c99da33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thechinfamily.hk/web/tc/managing-your-money/savings.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T13:11:14.000Z","msg":"人地學生哥得定額10萬，你就叫人月供，你真係覺得適合？"},{"pid":"305b97e37ef24d523fd8562bbe2c4b3c8e49ef92","tid":699110,"uid":15428,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1130ee2fb733aa233cfdf86538f760c8ad187e0c","tid":699110,"uid":83194,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"887974a9f13d9f99ce78d9fe34bf4760d4e28d0b","tid":699110,"uid":15428,"like":1,"dislike":22,"score":-21,"quote":{"pid":"c1d0211d7fed1edafcd3e72a6130c177f617593a","tid":699110,"uid":83194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:15:43.000Z","msg":"有咩plan咪拎出黎講"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T12:33:00.000Z","msg":"如果後生仔想儲得開心啲嘅有M嘅LV Plan<br />\n因為通常出面slogan就話「日儲$100年派$10000」<br />\n其實就係以每個月儲三千為例子，由第二年開始保證每年派一皮嘢派到一百歲<br />\n（供款年期可揀5/8/12/15年）<br />\nRef: <a href=\"https://www.manulife.com.hk/wps/wcm/connect/pws/fb4bb25e-0c02-43fb-8a31-0d28a418348b/Manulife_LaVie_Brochure_Chi_final_page.pdf?MOD=AJPERES\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.manulife.com.hk%2Fwps%2Fwcm%2Fconnect%2Fpws%2Ffb4bb25e-0c02-43fb-8a31-0d28a418348b%2FManulife_LaV